pageContext.claim: “The Radical Left, Do Nothing Democrats said they wanted to RUSH everything through to the Senate because 'President Trump is a threat to National Security' (they are vicious, will say anything!), but now they don't want to go fast anymore, they want to go very slowly. Liars!”
pageContext.analysis: The House of Representatives has passed dozens of bills, including an expansion of background checks for gun purchases, but they have largely died in the GOP-controlled Senate. On Dec. 18, House Speaker Nancy Pelosi (D-Calif.) said she has not submitted the articles of impeachment because, “we haven't seen anything that looks fair to us. So hopefully [the trial] will be fair.”
